reviewText: I grew up watching franklin and I knew instantly that I wanted my child to watch is as they grow up. So I bought it. Franklin is one of the best shows for kids to watch now days, it doesn't give off bad vibes nor do they say or do things that would give kids the bad idea. It's great! I prefer my child to watch this over the newer shows.
Cute Movie for Kids 3 and up
My grdau loves Franklin. This was perfect!
